text: Survivor Series (2011) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by WWE. It took place on November 20, 2011 at Madison Square Garden in New York City. It was the 25th Survivor Series event held by WWE and the third held at Madison Square Garden (after the 1996 and 2002 editions). In the main event, The Rock wrestled his first match since 2004. He and John Cena defeated The Miz and R-Truth. Also, CM Punk defeated Alberto Del Rio by submission to win his second WWE Championship.
